c_10/' target='_blank'><img  src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202008/04/5f2979bbbd9ce3158.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" alt="真人兽"/></a>真人兽</span></p><p itemprop="description">尺码参照着成人码选就行。</p><p itemprop="description">鞋舌有些磨脚，高脚背慎入（NIKE传统艺能<img alt="LD的第一双AJ，AIR JORDAN 1 MID SE (GS)" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/79.png" class="face" /> ）。<br/></p><p itemprop="description">鞋底偏硬，缓震靠<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/nanxiepeijian/" target="_blank">鞋垫</a>，脚感和Stan Smith差不多（LD说的<img alt="LD的第一双AJ，AIR JORDAN 1 MID SE (GS)" src="https://res.smzdm.com/images/emotions/80.png" class="face" /> ）。</p><h2 id="cl_3">总结</h2><p itemprop="description">绣花LO<a class="seo_link brand-hover" href="https://pinpai.smzdm.com/60712/" data-brandid="60712" target="_blank">GO</a>+年轻配色+倒闭款，适合第一次买AJ的小仙女，试试，图个乐。</p>
